# Feature catalog

This project was generated from feature packs. Dependencies are resolved automatically.

| Pack | Purpose | Requires |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `workspace` | Members, roles, and organization administration | auth, rbac |
| `content` | Editorial content and publishing | auth, rbac |
| `customers` | Companies and contacts | auth, rbac |
| `sales` | Pipelines, deals, and activities | customers |
| `audit` | Audit domain and viewer foundation | auth, rbac |
| `files` | S3-compatible file domain and upload foundation | auth, rbac |
| `email` | Provider-neutral message domain and development log adapter | jobs |
| `cache` | Application-owned cache seam with Redis and in-memory adapters | — |

CRM contacts are not login accounts. Workspace administrators create application users and assign roles. The retired `cms` and `crm` feature names are not supported.

## Bootstrap owner

On an empty production database, set `BOOTSTRAP_OWNER_EMAIL`, `BOOTSTRAP_OWNER_PASSWORD`, and `BOOTSTRAP_OWNER_ORGANIZATION_NAME` together to create the first owner with `platform.admin`. Partial configuration fails startup; the bootstrap never overwrites an existing account.
